metadata.value: By integrating a series of DeFi protocols, DeFis Network will form a strong network effect in the blockchain finance field in the future. The platform currency DFS will continue to capture the value generated by these DeFi protocols. DFS holders will continue to receive dividends from the agreement fee. Dividends are automatically executed through smart contracts, so that every holder can fairly share the dividends of DeFis Network development.

1) It is an exchange owned by all Dao communities. Community members provide liquidity for their own tokens and share 0.2% of the market-making fee income, and 0.05% goes into the community foundation as a fund reserve for the long-term development of community projects. 0.05% is injected into the MIXD repurchase and destruction fund!
2) It is an aggregation exchange on the EOS chain, which aggregates all DEXs to help users exchange the same digital assets for more tokens.
3) It is a node for all retail investors, and the node income is used to give the platform currency to all holders a fair income!
4) It is an algorithm-driven DEX. The platform currency of DEX is initially synthesized with existing assets, and whether it will be issued or destroyed in the future is determined by the algorithm and the market!

PIZZA-Lend is an EOS based money makey protocol. The protocol went live in June 2020 and has been iterated for several versions. Users can supply tokens to earn risk-less interest yield and borrow against their collateral with a fixed or variable interest rate. Both token suppliers and borrowers get PIZZA token rewards.
